{"tid":616039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》航拍港珠澳人工島 直擊近千石屎躉已被沖落海","createTime":"2018-04-04T00:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T00:45:10.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc32aa3fa416a7a76f670d1c5ee3dcbfa4cfdf00","tid":616039,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:24:57.000Z","msg":"在香港水域以外的港珠澳大橋「海底隧道東出入口人工島」，有大量保護人工島的防波堤石屎躉疑被大浪沖下海，專家擔心人工島出現不正常沉降，憂慮會影響海底隧道的結構安全，特區政府至今午仍未有回應事件。《蘋果》記者為了解真相，今午以航拍機直擊該人工島現場，發現人工島西邊防波提確有大量石屎躉(即Tetrapods消波塊)已被沖落海中，在距離岸邊約50米的海面範圍，估計有近千石屎躉沉在水中或半露出水面。<br />\n<br />\n由於大量防波提石躉已被沖下海中，人工島向西的一邊，露出了約5米高的人工島邊沿石屎壁結構，並完全「曝露」於空氣中，若大浪湧來，大量海水恐直接滲入人工島邊沿的縫隙，恐加劇其耗損。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/082442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F082442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ab4c10eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/082446_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F082446_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bdf05eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApple Daily"},{"pid":"1e05e03bddf913412b764e2cf9dd66d29609599a","tid":616039,"uid":59952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"好似想沉咁撚樣"},{"pid":"1b8e6c812faf612275dbcc66a0d3a41e58a0cfac","tid":616039,"uid":34661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"除左恭喜都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5f937b6bf7e43a542f8464a56149100a21d0e5","tid":616039,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93a0158f6508a329575c9425ec918c730849cf56","tid":616039,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re